cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CE, cs.AI 

This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to predict heart failure readmission from clinical notes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and information retrieval. The paper also uses deep learning models, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves healthcare applications, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science). Finally, the paper uses predictive models, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
